00:05.900 --> 00:08.100
(man) IT'S YOUR MOTHER'S
BELOVED DOG HALSTON.

00:08.100 --> 00:11.300
PARTIAL RETROGRADE AMNESIA?
THE LAST THING
ALEXIS REMEMBERS

00:11.300 --> 00:13.400
IS MOM'S BIRTHDAY PARTY
TWO YEARS AGO.

00:13.400 --> 00:15.100
WITH ALEXIS
STILL IN THE HOSPITAL,

00:15.100 --> 00:17.200
I WANT TO POSTPONE
THE WEDDING.

00:17.200 --> 00:18.300
YOUR FATHER WAS A HERO.

00:18.300 --> 00:19.500
?????

00:19.500 --> 00:20.800
(Justin) NO, I'M NOT.

00:20.800 --> 00:23.100
IT LOOKS LIKE WE'LL NEED
AN INTERN AROUND THE OFFICE

00:23.100 --> 00:25.100
FOR THE NEXT COUPLE OF WEEKS
BEFORE SCHOOL STARTS.

00:25.100 --> 00:26.300
OH, MY GOD!

00:26.300 --> 00:28.300
AND MY DAD'S
ILL STUCK IN MEXICO.

00:28.300 --> 00:30.300
(Ignacio) I KILLED IGNACIO SUAREZ?

00:30.300 --> 00:31.300
????

00:32.299 --> 00:34.900
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING
ABOUT THIS BABY OF YOURS.

00:34.900 --> 00:37.700
CHRISTINA TOLD ME ABOUT CHARLIE,
THAT SHE CHEATED ON ME.

00:37.700 --> 00:39.800
CHARLIE WAS THE ONLY REASON
WE COULDN'T BE TOGETHER.

00:39.800 --> 00:41.400
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU,
BETTY.

00:44.400 --> 00:46.000
HENRY,'RE DRUNK.

00:46.000 --> 00:47.700
(slurs)
AND YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

00:51.800 --> 00:53.200
HENRY, STOP.

00:56.300 --> 01:00.200
LOOK, THIS IS NOT HOW I EVER
PICTURED US BEING TOGETHER.

01:00.500 --> 01:04.500
YOU'RE DRUNK
OF... WINE COOLERS.

01:04.500 --> 01:07.200
"MELON AND APRICOT."
IT'S GROSS.

01:08.100 --> 01:09.100
YOU'RE RIGHT.

01:10.600 --> 01:12.100
I'M A TERRIBLE PERSON.

01:13.400 --> 01:14.900
I HAD A CIGARETTE, TOO.

01:15.700 --> 01:18.500
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME ABOUT
CHARLIE AND THAT DENTIST?

01:19.100 --> 01:19.700
I...

01:21.900 --> 01:23.800
LOOK, I'VE WANTED TO.
I JUST...

01:24.900 --> 01:27.300
STARTED THINKING THAT MAYBE
IT WASN'T THE RIGHT THING TO DO.

01:27.300 --> 01:29.400
HENRY,
THERE IS A BABY INVOLVED.

01:29.400 --> 01:32.100
WHICH MIGHT NOT BE MINE.
BUT MAYBE IT IS,

01:32.400 --> 01:35.200
AND I-I CAN'T GET
MY HEART BROKEN AGAIN.

01:35.600 --> 01:37.400
IT'S LIKE THE WHOLE WORLD
IS TELLING US

01:37.400 --> 01:38.700
WE SHOULDN'T BE TOGETHER.

01:40.900 --> 01:42.700
WE'RE LIKE
MELON AND APRICOT.

01:42.700 --> 01:45.000
LOOK,
I DO WANT TO BE WITH YOU.

01:45.900 --> 01:47.200
I DO, IT'S...

01:47.600 --> 01:51.300
IT'S JUST--
WE DON'T KNOW WHOSE BABY IT IS,

01:52.300 --> 01:53.700
AND WE JUST HAVE TO WAIT,

01:55.600 --> 01:56.800
AND I CAN DO THAT

01:58.500 --> 01:59.700
IF YOU CAN.

